  "message": "fuzz(signature_parsing): extend corpus with 15 ufunc signature seeds\n\nAdds coverage for:\n- Dimension expansion/reduction: (a)->(a,a), (a,a)->(a)\n- Multi-operand chains: (i,j),(j,k),(k,l)->(i,l)\n- Ellipsis variants: (...)->(), (...)\n- Mixed arity patterns: (a),(b,c),(d)->(a,b,c,d)\n- Named dimensions: (dim1,dim2)->(dim1,dim2)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
